blog NEWS

2003-01-05 -- 1.0

* Release 1.0. Minor changes from 0.1.8, but stable enough for a release.

2002-06-24 -- 0.1.8

* Switched shell back to bash; more politically correct.
* Cleaned up a few things.
* Fixed a no-eol-at-eof bug.

2002-02-27 -- 0.1.7

* Fixed potential bug when the number of entries exceeds 100.

* --edit and --delete do not automatically rebuild any longer.

2002-02-07 -- 0.1.6

* General cluestick changes.

2001-11-24 -- 0.1.5

* Uses perl scripts for substitution now, not confusing and hacked awk
  scripts.

2001-11-18 -- 0.1.4

* Switched shell to ksh.
* --list and --show options added.
* configure script added.
* Imported into CVS.

2001-08-26 -- 0.1.3

* --verbose now more verbose.
* Added manpage.

2001-08-01 -- 0.1.2

* First public alpha release.
* Put together informational files, sample config file.
* First live test on my own web site.

2001-07-30 -- 0.1.1

* Pre-alpha non-public release.
